
<Lesson stage="2" page="12" type="Reading Check">
<APageParagraph activityIntroClip="uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3"  pencil="p3" skipIntro="true">
	<paragraph>
		<sentence>
			<text>CR</text>
			<clip></clip>
		</sentence>
		<sentence>
			<text>Ryan and Hunter were resting on the hillside on their way home from baseball practice.</text>
			<clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
		</sentence>
		<sentence>
			<text>Hunter suddenly pointed down the valley.</text>
			<clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
		</sentence>
    <sentence>
         <text>"Look at that idiot with that bus.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
   </sentence>
   <sentence>
         <text>Can you imagine bringing a school bus down a country road like this?</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
   </sentence>
   <sentence>
         <text>There's no room for it.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
   </sentence>
   <sentence>
         <text>What if something comes the other way?"</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
   </sentence>
  </paragraph>
  <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Just then they saw a car coming much too fast in the other direction.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The school bus and the car went towards each other without either driver knowing it.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The bus and the car almost hit each other at the sharp bend.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The car turned right and smashed partly through a gate and partly through a fence.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The two friends snapped into action.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>      
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
       <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
	   <sentence>
		  <text>Ryan tried to phone for help, but there was no signal for his cell phone in such a remote area.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
       <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>   
      <sentence>
         <text>Ryan and Hunter ran faster than they had ever run before.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>They were scared of children being hurt and what they might find.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Hunter remained by the crash, while Ryan sprinted to the nearest town.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>It was a good thing he was fit.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>At the coffee shop he dialled 911 and got through right away.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>"There’s been an accident about a mile down the road.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>A school bus and a car are smashed up and some people are hurt.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	</sentence>
     <sentence>
        <text>This is an emergency."</text>
        <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The operator said, "Tell me where the crash happened and we'll get help to you real soon."</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>CR</text>
		  <clip></clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>CR</text>
		  <clip></clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
         <text>"I'll go back and tell them," replied Ryan, and he was soon running back up the road.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
</APageParagraph>
</Lesson>
